        "description": "## Description\n<strong>SUMMARY</strong>\nDataset contains SF311 cases created since 7/1/2008 with location information. \n\n<strong>UPDATE PROCESS</strong>\nThis dataset updates daily.\n\n<strong>HOW TO USE THIS DATASET</strong>\nDownload data using 'export' button to the right. For more information on this dataset, visit the  <u><a href=\"https://sfdigitalservices.gitbook.io/dataset-explainers/311-cases\">FAQ page</a></u>.\n\n<strong>Want to map the data in your neighborhood?</strong> \nCheck out https://sf.connect.socrata.com/\n\nFor more information about Open311, see http://www.open311.org/.\n"
